{"tid":2158680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國停止為香港警察提供訓練","createTime":"2020-08-15T23:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T01:59:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"96ee84fd348687bb950936b55f175d432ba42329","tid":2158680,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T23:28:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/15/uk-suspends-military-training-for-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Faug%2F15%2Fuk-suspends-military-training-for-hong-kong-police-force&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b78fd8d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/15/uk-suspends-military-training-for-hong-kong-police-force</a>"},{"pid":"a55a40b79a20dbb20a35807b4311403a91f75255","tid":2158680,"uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T23:29:09.000Z","msg":"The government has barred UK military personnel from training the Hong Kong police force and two other organisations amid worsening relations with China.<br />\nBoth the army and the RAF run limited drill instructor programmes for Hong Kong&rsquo;s police force, its Government Flying Service and its Sea Cadet Corps, but these have now been put on hold, the Ministry of Defence told the Observer.<br />\nThe UK says the decision is being taken because of the Covid-19 crisis. But a spokesman confirmed the contracts will be reviewed when the pandemic is over."},{"pid":"6238fa22a5f9a57c00d8fc10dbb79f51d8dd8f99","tid":2158680,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T23:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0d64bd6f